title: Schubert - Symphony No. 9, Rosamunde Overture - Abbado, COE
description:
Schubert: Symphony No. 9 and the Rosamunde Overture.

Schubert's Ninth Symphony, "The Great," and Rosamunde Overture, as recorded by Claudio Abbado and the Chamber Orchestra of Europe and released by DG in 1988. These are perfect interpretations and performances. As well, these recordings are the first based on the autograph manuscript.

Please enjoy.

MP3 @ 320
